{"tid":471660,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"告別真男人！鐵血後衛麥薩斯宣佈退役！","createTime":"2017-11-17T12:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T09:19:12.000Z","uid":41710,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fa7ff827ab0f92ea0a3ab0dc465965b7dd38576f","tid":471660,"uid":41710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T12:54:59.000Z","msg":"麥薩斯接受法國足球訪問時宣布退役，他明確表示自己不會再繼續職業生涯。<br />\n<br />\n麥薩斯表示：&ldquo;我接到過幾份高薪的合約邀請，包括來自於土耳其、中國、美國、墨西哥和印度的球隊。我有機會繼續踢球，也考慮過重返意大利。不過考慮到我的家庭，我的孩子，我還是決定過一段比較簡單的生活，結束自己的職業生涯。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;我覺得自己已經無法再為歐洲頂級豪門效力。在這樣的情況下你會做兩種選擇，一是為了錢去一家比較小眾的聯賽，二就是選擇退役。我覺得退役比較適合我，儘管我覺得自己還能再在賽場上征戰一兩個賽季。我不喜歡當那種拿錢不出力的騙子，說假話時我會不自覺地眨眼睛。&rdquo;</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1982年出生的麥薩斯司職後衛，國籍法國，職業生涯先後效力於歐塞爾、羅馬、米蘭，2004年以700萬歐元加盟羅馬，代表球隊7個賽季出戰155場聯賽，入11球。2011年夏天，自由轉會米蘭，總共代表米蘭在意甲出場81場，入6球。此外也代表法國隊出戰了2012年歐洲盃。<br />\n<br />\n以後無得睇你踢波了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3003d44fd2d81251b732f6438539d32caed23472","tid":471660,"uid":41710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T12:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/205946_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F205946_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a048c19a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1dff8b88d9019bedab1b373e55a0cdb73e2eed5","tid":471660,"uid":41710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:03:16.000Z","msg":"重溫Mexes世界波合集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FWkYoaXVG5I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFWkYoaXVG5I&d=oC5AbjMi%2BH1TB6WHdjrt%2Fb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=16086bc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FWkYoaXVG5I</a>"},{"pid":"05614d390287019315704ca231612dbb562a50d6","tid":471660,"uid":89607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:03:42.000Z","msg":"真男人...以為佢比人切咗"},{"pid":"bab7388c09562f842235c65917dfed95f4b767b5","tid":471660,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"告別真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c420ac5942cadabea5b7603263298dfe69fe0b27","tid":471660,"uid":19556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21539990b56b820de55e1f90fa536f8878dcb8fa","tid":471660,"uid":41710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T15:11:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真男人...以為佢比人切咗</blockquote><br />\nching係咪有咩誤會"},{"pid":"d24b6291f8960074ed46102f019d32e1aa589a0b","tid":471660,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T17:06:13.000Z","msg":"@alex buttner"},{"pid":"1b452e513a53568e0c7280b7e797b4371e81f2ea","tid":471660,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T17:08:48.000Z","msg":"mexes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2021d98454ee3688c19414666ee2a06820746bc","tid":471660,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T17:09:40.000Z","msg":"我會懷念你.."},{"pid":"7798a9b1020ae89d2c64983347ead7b1ef5b5999","tid":471660,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:01:51.000Z","msg":"我不喜歡當那種拿錢不出力的騙子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7f09a26b7f6c044d8e5888eb64a3df5396a443","tid":471660,"uid":13718,"lik